ce Plugin Manager** (pkg/kubelet/pluginmanager/plugin_manager.go): The PluginManager interface manages device and plugin registration/deregistration. The pluginManager implementation (created via NewPluginManager) runs asynchronous loops using a reconciler pattern to track plugin state and trigger registration/deregistration operations. This is critical for GPU, device, and other plugin integrations.\n\nAll these components are located in pkg/kubelet and its subdirectories, with ownership confirmed in the OWNERS file under sig-node-approvers and sig-node-reviewers."
